{"tid":682480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[18禁] 網紅才爆「床戰乾爹」淫片     又有自拍床照外流瘋傳","createTime":"2018-05-29T02:19:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T03:48:22.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"492a14d9d9f12dfad11145f6010fefe74668e635","tid":682480,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:19:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/felD6Cmm6-g/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FfelD6Cmm6-g%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=84c29466&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國網紅馮提莫因「床戰乾爹」照片和影片瘋傳的風波，讓她一夕之間爆紅，除被爆出隱婚陪睡醜聞外，更曾有土豪一夜打賞900萬人民幣而躍升中國的「主播一姐」，不料一波未平，一波又起，28日被爆出與一名男子甜蜜自拍床照，再次引發熱議。<br />\n<br />\n微博上有一名八卦版主，今日（28日）曝光了馮提莫與一名陌生男子甜蜜的床上合影，照片中的馮提莫對著鏡頭自然燦笑。更有網友爆出，照片中的男子已婚有家室，且發現該男子極有可能為馮提莫長期關注對象，而晉升成為親暱關係之人，對此，許多粉絲希望等馮提莫本人親自出面回應後，再下結論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2018/05/28/phpj6gJxW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2Fphpj6gJxW.jpg&h=b4607701&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2439708\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2439708&d=Am5SbhvUSQ1Wlx40sPgUt9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=4772d14a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2439708&h=6ffae930\" target=\"_blank\">http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2439708</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f15c31e33a38a3482b40ec5e20dc7671aaf57e","tid":682480,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:21:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74e914f96d0480b01c740e5231e1a98d451fad35","tid":682480,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T02:32:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/